{
  "$comment": "Registry of 3D models and the mesh-name -> layer mapping for each. Mesh names are NEVER hardcoded in app code; when a real GLB replaces a placeholder, only update meshLayerMap here. Patterns are exact names or prefixes ending in '*' (longest pattern wins) and are matched against each mesh's own name and then its ancestor group names. The vehicle uses the CC-BY Sketchfab W221 by Black Snow (prepared via scripts/prepare-w221.mjs) plus generated wheels/harness (vehicle-extras.glb); the engine model stays procedural because the kit has no engine internals. The procedural vehicle.glb remains available as a fallback.",
